{
  "name": "hp-compaq-kastner-insight1-a5a4e0",
  "title": "The HP-Compaq Merger: If There's the Will, There's a Way",
  "description": "Aberdeen InSight by Peter Kastner analyzing the proposed HP-Compaq merger announced September 2001. Identifies significant product overlap across servers (Intel/Windows, Unix, Itanium, Linux) and services, and warns that customers are confused and concerned about a merger focused on 'more' rather than 'better.' Argues that sustained outward customer focus \u2014 via strong marketing and sales retraining \u2014 is the key to merger success, and that without it Dell, IBM, and Sun would be the beneficiaries. This is an independent source file (Archive-2) for the same insight as 2001-hp-compaq-kastner-insight1-d6dc38 from Archive-1; processed separately as instructed.",
